SELECT uses_knowledge_graph, COUNT(evaluation_metric) AS count_evaluation_metric 
FROM cspaper 
WHERE reasoning_depth = 'multi-hop' 
GROUP BY uses_knowledge_graph;

SELECT data_modality, AVG(baseline_amount) AS avg_baseline_amount 
FROM cspaper 
WHERE application_domain != 'Education' OR use_agent = 'Yes' 
GROUP BY data_modality;
